HEADWORD: Dahlia
<hw>Dah"lia</hw> <pr>(d⟦aum⟧l"y⟦adot⟧ <i>or</i> d⟦amac⟧l"y⟦adot⟧; 277,
106)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Dahlias</plw>
<pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Named after Andrew <etsep>Dahl</etsep> a
Swedish botanist.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of plants native
